description.en: Nucleus is a Stable Supply token which gives devs access to dev teams and marketing teams to launch or run your token and exposure to exclusive buyers who will help your token grow. For Nucleus holders who are not current or future token owners, access to insider information on based launches and priority access to contracts at launches backed and audited by the team behind Nucleus. A portion of the fees from the launches managed by Nucleus will be added to Nucleus Token liquidity as well.
